<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_Form_Element-&gt;setAttrib() exists, but there is no way to complete remove an attribute.  The use case here is adding 'disabled' and then only being able to set it to an empty string, which still means disabled, rather than removing the attribute all together.</p>

    </div>
